  "short_description": "SEDAP! is a vibrant couch co-op cooking adventure where you and a friend work together to prepare iconic Southeast Asian dishes in a colourful hand-painted fantasy world inspired by the region’s cuisine and culture. Team up, hunt for food, coordinate kitchen chaos, and master delicious favourites!",
